Mleczkowo  is a settlement in the administrative district of Gmina Ryn, within Giżycko County, Warmian-Masurian Voivodeship, in northern Poland. It lies approximately  north of Ryn,  south-west of Giżycko, and  east of the regional capital Olsztyn.
